<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10084917>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Platystoma meridionale lectotype ♂ (HMNH): a—habitus, lateral right view; b, c—head (b—lateral right, c— anterior view); d—mesonotum, dorsal view; e, f—wing (e—left, f—right); g—abdomen, dorsal view; h—labels. Scale bar unavailable. Photos by Valery Korneyev (except e—from Hendel 1913)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10084917/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10084919>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Platystoma meridionale lectotype ♂ Platystoma idia (MNHNP): a—habitus, lateral left view; b, c—head (b— lateral right, c—anterior view); d—mesonotum, dorsal view; e, f—wing (e—left, f—right); g—abdomen, dorsal view; h— labels. Scale bar unavailable. Photos by Emmanuel Delfosse." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10084919/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10084921>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Platystoma meridionale ♂ (a–c) and ♀ (d–g) from Rif and Middle Atlas, Morocco (HMNH): a–b, d–f—habitus, c—abdomen (a, d—lateral left, b, e—dorsal, c, f—ventral view); g—head (anterior view) h—wing i–k—fore, mid and hind legs, respectively; l—flies on animal faeces. Scale bar unavailable. Photos by Younes El Harym." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10084921/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10084923>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Platystoma meridionale ♂ (a–c) and ♀ (d–e) from Rif and Middle Atlas, Morocco (HMNH), genitalia: a— epandrium and hypandrium, right lateral view; b—ejaculatory apodeme, c—phallus (detached); d—aculeus (ventral view); e—spermathecae. Scale bar unavailable. Photos by Younes El Harym." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10084923/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

